(686, 'DIORBLUSH PRECIOUS ROCKS - Christmas 2017 Limited Edition', 'dior', '0.0', 0, 'blush', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#EF8687\",\"colour_name\":\"864 Precious Rocks\"}]', 'The new limited-edition Diorblush showcases every facet of the Precious Rocks collection. Printed with a prismatic motif that reflects that of a precious stone, its sheer, peach colour blends seamlessly with your skin to deliver a fresh, crystal-clear complexion.', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/version-5.1432748111912/resize-image/ep/0/390/100/0/packshots%252FPDG_Y0715928_F071592864.jpg', '2017-12-03T23:22:36.467Z', '2017-12-23T20:58:48.998Z', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/en_gb/fragrance-beauty/makeup/look-exclusives/precious-rocks-collection/pr-preciousrockslook-y0715928_f071592864-vibrant-colour-powderblush.html'),
(687, 'Diorskin Rosy Glow', 'dior', '32.0', 0, 'blush', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#F1C0D7\",\"colour_name\":\"001 Petal\"}]', 'Rosy Glow reacts to the moisture in the skin to bring a delicate flush of colour to the cheeks. The fresh and luminous color upon application develops into a rosy blush to suit each individual complexion for an incredibly natural, custom healthy glow that lasts all day.', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/version-5.1432748111912/resize-image/ep/0/390/100/0/packshots%252FPDG_Y0715100.jpg', '2017-12-03T23:22:37.243Z', '2017-12-23T20:58:49.221Z', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/en_gb/fragrance-beauty/makeup/face/blush/pr-blush-y0715100_f071510001-healthy-glow-booster-blush.html'),
(688, 'Backstage Eye Prime', 'dior', '22.5', 0, 'eyeshadow', '[]', 'The first eye primer from Dior Backstage. Its smoothing and unifying action immediately corrects and prepares the eyelid for maximum colour intensity.', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/version-5.1432748111912/resize-image/ep/0/390/100/0/packshots%252FPDG_Y0146000_032016.jpg', '2017-12-03T23:22:40.273Z', '2017-12-23T20:58:50.046Z', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/en_gb/fragrance-beauty/makeup/eyes/eyeshadows/pr-eyeshadows-y0146000-10h-color-locking-and-crease-preventing-eyelid-primer.html'),
(689, 'Diorshow Fusion Mono', 'dior', '25.5', 0, 'eyeshadow', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#8B4E78\",\"colour_name\":\"981\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#826A73\",\"colour_name\":\"881 Hypnotique\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#BD9E9B\",\"colour_name\":\"771\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#BD9171\",\"colour_name\":\"661 Mu00e9tu00e9ore\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#93867A\",\"colour_name\":\"381 Millenium\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#EDE9E6\",\"colour_name\":\"001 Lune\"}]', 'A weightless texture that blends into the skin and dresses the eye in velvety colour. In a single step, it creates an even and intense matte finish for a professional makeup effect.', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/version-5.1432748111912/resize-image/ep/0/390/100/0/packshots%252FPDG_Y0148300_F014830821_012016.jpg', '2017-12-03T23:22:40.725Z', '2017-12-23T20:58:50.521Z', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/en_gb/fragrance-beauty/makeup/eyes/eyeshadows/pr-eyeshadows-y0148300-long-wear-professional-mirror-shine-eyeshadow.html'),
(690, 'Diorshow Fusion Mono Matte', 'dior', '0.0', 0, 'eyeshadow', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#E5BAA8\",\"colour_name\":\"721 Songe\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#363A3E\",\"colour_name\":\"091 Nocturne\"}]', 'A weightless texture that blends into the skin and dresses the eye in velvety colour. In a single step, it creates an even and intense matte finish for a professional makeup effect.', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/version-5.1432748111912/resize-image/ep/0/390/100/0/packshots%252FPDG_Y0148310_F014831761_012016.jpg', '2017-12-03T23:22:41.944Z', '2017-12-23T20:58:50.955Z', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/en_gb/fragrance-beauty/makeup/eyes/eyeshadows/pr-eyeshadows-y0148310-long-wear-professional-eyeshadow.html'),
(692, '5 COULEURS', 'dior', '45.0', 0, 'eyeshadow', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#D1BFBA\",\"colour_name\":\"797 Feel\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E0CBC8\",\"colour_name\":\"777 Exalt\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E2CCC7\",\"colour_name\":\"767 Inflame\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D9CDCE\",\"colour_name\":\"757 Dream\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D8C9BC\",\"colour_name\":\"657 Expose\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#DCCBC3\",\"colour_name\":\"647 Undress\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#DACFC9\",\"colour_name\":\"567 Adore\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E6D8D1\",\"colour_name\":\"537 Touch\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#CFD1D1\",\"colour_name\":\"357 Electrify\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#C5C9D1\",\"colour_name\":\"277 Defy\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D9CED4\",\"colour_name\":\"157 Magnify\"}]', 'An icon of the Dior look and a concentration of expertise in terms of colour and visual effects, the 5 Couleurs palette is reinvented. More creative than ever, with stronger pigments and richer effects, it allows women to explore every facet of colour and express every aspect of their personality. With the 5 Couleurs palette, self-expression is unlimited, creativity is unleashed and colour is more audacious than ever.', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/version-5.1432748111912/resize-image/ep/0/390/100/0/packshots%252FPDG_Y0148410.jpg', '2017-12-03T23:22:47.200Z', '2017-12-23T20:58:51.384Z', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/en_gb/fragrance-beauty/makeup/eyes/eyeshadows/pr-eyeshadows-y0148410-high-fidelity-colours-effects-eyeshadow-palette.html'),
(693, '5 COULEURS PRECIOUS ROCKS - Christmas 2017 Limited Edition', 'dior', '43.5', 0, 'eyeshadow', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#DCC1BF\",\"colour_name\":\"857 Ruby\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D7D8CC\",\"colour_name\":\"347 Emerald\"}]', 'Emblematic of Dior eye makeup, this winter, the 5 Couleurs palette has been reinterpreted in two limited editions featuring ruby and emerald tones.', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/version-5.1432748111912/resize-image/ep/0/390/100/0/packshots%252FPDG_Y0148228_F014822857_v2.jpg', '2017-12-03T23:22:49.724Z', '2017-12-23T20:58:51.579Z', 'https://www.dior.com/beauty/en_gb/fragrance-beauty/makeup/look-exclusives/precious-rocks-collection/pr-preciousrockslook-y0148223-high-fidelity-colours-effects-eyeshadow-palette.html'),
