(909, 'Dark Circle Concealer', 'nyx', '6.0', 0, 'foundation', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#A96540\",\"colour_name\":\"Deep\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E5895A\",\"colour_name\":\"Medium\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#EA9B70\",\"colour_name\":\"Light\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#ECAA87\",\"colour_name\":\"Fair\"}]', 'A serious solution for one of beauty’s most challenging problems! No fancy names just a product that can be counted on to do the job. The product glides on without looking thick or obvious. The subtle hint of orange counteracts the appearance of dark circles while natural skin-toned pigments work in unison to provide the ultimate coverage.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw477d3d9a/ProductImages/Face/Dark_Circle_Concealer/800897822958_darkcircleconcealer_light_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:28:17.702Z', '2017-12-24T02:30:13.878Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dark-circle-concealer/NYX_133.html?cgid=concealer'),
(910, 'Wonder Pencil', 'nyx', '4.5', 0, 'eyeliner', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#AF8F76\",\"colour_name\":\"Deep\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#C49D7E\",\"colour_name\":\"Medium\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E5C19F\",\"colour_name\":\"Light\"}]', 'Wonder Pencil…the essential pencil that fulfills all of your beauty desires. Conquer 3 critical make-up tasks with one product: CONCEAL flaws and blemishes with creamy precision; LINE your lips against lipstick bleeding and fading; and BRIGHTEN your eyes along the water line. Will wonders never cease? Not with the Wonder Pencil in your bag!', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw5e345fad/ProductImages/Face/Wonder_Pencil/wonderpencil_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:28:18.879Z', '2017-12-24T02:32:16.275Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/wonder-pencil/NYX_091.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(911, 'Conceal, Correct, Contour Palette', 'nyx', '12.0', 0, 'foundation', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#F1F2F4\",\"colour_name\":\"Deep\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#FDF9F6\",\"colour_name\":\"Medium\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#FFFEFC\",\"colour_name\":\"Light\"}]', 'Color-match your skin using our perfecting and correcting palettes to conceal, correct, or contour. With six shades to choose from in each set you can cover up problem spots even out imperfections and accentuate your best features in a flash. Use these buildable colors on their own or combine them to create the ideal tone.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwbef45c94/ProductImages/Face/Conceal_Correct_Contour_Palette/800897831479_concealcorrectcontourpalette_light_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:28:19.928Z', '2017-12-24T02:30:15.919Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/conceal-correct-contour-palette/NYX_170.html?cgid=concealer'),
