(913, 'Powder Blush', 'nyx', '5.0', 0, 'bronzer', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#C27B67\",\"colour_name\":\"Terra Cotta\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D19E9D\",\"colour_name\":\"Angel\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#AB0A33\",\"colour_name\":\"Red\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E07F88\",\"colour_name\":\"Pinched\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#BA356C\",\"colour_name\":\"Pinky\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#DD7F97\",\"colour_name\":\"Rose Garden\"}]', 'Our pressed powder blush delivers sheer silky color that glides on easily blends beautifully and creates a natural glow. The formula is richly-pigmented and lasts for hours.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw12ca4942/ProductImages/Face/Powder_Blush/powderblush_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:28:25.043Z', '2017-12-24T02:30:52.742Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/powder-blush/NYX_009.html?cgid=bronzer'),
