(943, 'Epic Ink Liner', 'nyx', '8.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[]', 'Live for super-sharp wing inspo? Don’t just “like” all your faves, draw ’em yourself using Epic Ink Liner. Featuring a slender and supple brush tip, this intensely pigmented, waterproof pen lets you achieve black liquid lines effortlessly. Every stroke is unbelievably fluid for a defined finish. Control the thickness of your lines by pressing down just a touch. Fine and natural, broad and bold—the look is always up to you!', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw1c0eb02f/ProductImages/2017/Eyes/Epic_Ink_Liner/800897085605_epicinkliner_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:37.256Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:37.606Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/epic-ink-liner/NYX_409.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(944, 'Studio Liquid Liner', 'nyx', '4.5', 0, 'eyeliner', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#2A2A2A\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Black\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#4A4A4A\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Smokey Gray\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#AAAAAA\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Silver\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D2982C\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Gold\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#75401E\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Coffee\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#693C8F\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Plum Purple\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#6953A8\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Purple\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#1F5BBD\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Blue\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#1078AF\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Sapphire\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#61A9CF\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Sky Blue\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#52A749\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Green\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#EDB3B2\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Pink\"}]', 'Transform your look in seconds with this super-pigmented eyeliner that highlights eyes with an electrifying stroke of color. The fine brush tip allows for precision application and can be used to create lines of varying thickness. Go subtle or go glam.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw1a631541/ProductImages/Eyes/Studio_Liquid_Liner/studioliquidliner_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:37.926Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:38.426Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/studio-liquid-liner/NYX_028.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(945, 'White Liquid Liner', 'nyx', '7.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[]', 'Get bright-eyed in a blink with our opaque water resistant liquid white liner. Perfect for the lash or waterline the precision brush helps create a defined white line leaving you with standout eyes and a lasting matte finish.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw0fd19ef1/ProductImages/Eyes/White_Liquid_Liner/whiteliquidliner_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:39.840Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:40.217Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/white-liquid-liner/NYX_188.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(947, 'Vinyl Liquid Liner', 'nyx', '7.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[]', 'Rock and roll with our pure shine liquid liner! The extra fine flexible brush helps ensure a flawless even line with a high gloss finish.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw9723d9ae/ProductImages/Eyes/Vinyl_Liquid_Liner/vinylliquidliner_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:42.089Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:42.474Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/vinyl-liquid-liner/NYX_187.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(948, 'Colored Felt Tip Liner', 'nyx', '10.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#4E2D1C\",\"colour_name\":\"Chocolate Brown\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#363636\",\"colour_name\":\"Grey\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#F9F9F9\",\"colour_name\":\"White\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#0B5489\",\"colour_name\":\"Cobalt Blue\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#052363\",\"colour_name\":\"Royal Blue\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#003D37\",\"colour_name\":\"Teal\"}]', 'Line your lids with style and rock a range of captivating looks with our new Colored Felt Tip Liners. Available in six brilliant shades, each liquid liner features a precision felt-tip brush and an easy-to-use “grip zone” for precise, clean, pro-level application every time.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwa801b855/ProductImages/2016/Eyes/Colored_Felt_Tip_Liner/coloredfelttipliner_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:43.106Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:43.448Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/colored-felt-tip-liner/NYX_307.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(949, 'The Curve', 'nyx', '15.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[]', 'The original – The Curve! An innovative ergonomic shape that makes applying liquid liner mistake-proof. The grip zone provides just the right hold to make application precise secure and best of all...beautifully effortless results.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw6a4af1d6/ProductImages/Eyes/The_Curve/thecurve_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:44.277Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:44.655Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/the-curve/NYX_084.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(950, 'Felt Tip Liner', 'nyx', '9.5', 0, 'eyeliner', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#202020\",\"colour_name\":\"Jet Black\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#49201A\",\"colour_name\":\"Dark Brown\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#131313\",\"colour_name\":\"Extreme Black\"}]', 'Our Felt Tip Eyeliner gives you the ultimate control in creating bold and precise lines in 3 opulent shades—extreme black dark brown and jet black. The eyeliner marker releases the ideal amount of ink for decidedly dramatic eyes.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw16b77618/ProductImages/Eyes/Felt_Tip_Liner/feltipliner_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:44.985Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:45.557Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/felt-tip-liner/NYX_024.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(951, 'Super Skinny Eye Marker', 'nyx', '9.5', 0, 'eyeliner', '[]', 'The micro-fine felt tip on this eyeliner means you can use it for everything from filling in your eyelash line to a subtle cat-eye look.The eye marker application is flawless and the results are fabulous.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwea7c51df/ProductImages/Eyes/Super_Skinny_Eye_Marker/superskinnyeyemarker_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:46.060Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:46.619Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/super-skinny-eye-marker/NYX_027.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(952, 'Super Fat Eye Marker', 'nyx', '10.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[]', 'Here’s a real magic marker: The extra wide felt tip eye liner is perfect for creating a dramatic cat-eye look. The eye marker application is smooth and the striking results are long-lasting.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw8c640821/ProductImages/Eyes/Super_Fat_Eye_Marker/superfateyemarker_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:46.839Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:47.269Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/super-fat-eye-marker/NYX_026.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(953, 'Collection Chocolate', 'nyx', '6.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#442B24\",\"colour_name\":\"Liquid Brown Liner\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#281409\",\"colour_name\":\"Skinny Brown Liner\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E7E7DF\",\"colour_name\":\"Kohl Kajal Brown Liner\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#36251B\",\"colour_name\":\"Satin Finish Brown Liner\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#27160F\",\"colour_name\":\"Matte Brown Liner\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#3B2C25\",\"colour_name\":\"Glossy Brown Liner\"}]', 'What’s better than a guilt-free treat! Feast your eyes on our Collection Chocolate in 6 of our most delectable liners. The mouthwatering formula is smudge proof and comes in satin matte glossy or liquid.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwbccef58f/ProductImages/Eyes/Collection_Chocolate/collectionchocolate_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:47.604Z', '2017-12-24T02:32:22.990Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/collection-chocolate/NYX_090.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(954, 'Strictly Vinyl Eyeliner', 'nyx', '7.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#31443E\",\"colour_name\":\"Savvy\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#493966\",\"colour_name\":\"Extra\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#792B29\",\"colour_name\":\"Hazy\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#593E35\",\"colour_name\":\"Alliance\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#32486D\",\"colour_name\":\"Visceral\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#443844\",\"colour_name\":\"Crone\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#424146\",\"colour_name\":\"Dauntless\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#2B3043\",\"colour_name\":\"Anchor\"}]', 'Ready to give Strictly Vinyl Eyeliner a spin? Take your pick from the eight epic colors included in our vibrant catalog. Featuring a flexible and slim brush, this high-shine liquid eyeliner glides on effortlessly and delivers an intensely lacquered look you’ll want to rock again…and again!', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw1498d09f/ProductImages/2018/Eyes/Strictly_Vinyl_Eyeliner/strictlyvinyleyeliner_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:48.739Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:49.218Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/strictly-vinyl-eyeliner/NYX_600.html?cgid=eyeliner'),
(955, 'Two Timer Dual Ended Eyeliner', 'nyx', '10.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[]', 'Having it all is possible with this incredibly edgy new makeup weapon. The combination of the precision of liquid liner with the ease of application of a kohl pencil is the perfect match to create a variety of dramatic looks. When the cat eye meets the smoldering intensity of a smoky eye look - who knows where the night will take you?', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwcd8987df/ProductImages/Eyes/Two_Timer_Dual_Ended_Eyeliner/twotimerdualendedeyeliner_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:31:51.431Z', '2017-12-24T02:31:52.376Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/two-timer-dual-ended-eyeliner/NYX_135.html?cgid=eyeliner');
