(985, 'Eyebrow Push-Up Bra', 'nyx', '10.0', 0, 'eyebrow', '[]', 'Play up your natural assets with this dual-sided pencil that delivers sensual eyebrows in just a few minutes. Use the universally flattering brow pencil to draw and fill in your arches and the highlighting end to lift and brighten. Like the LBD of pencils the effect is captivating and undeniably sexy.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwadba3ae6/ProductImages/Eyes/Eyebrow_Push_Up_Bra/eyebrowpushupbra_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:32:55.489Z', '2017-12-24T02:32:55.884Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/eyebrow-push-up-bra/NYX_030.html?cgid=brows'),
(986, 'Eyebrow Kit With Stencil', 'nyx', '15.0', 0, 'eyebrow', '[]', 'Our all-in-one eyebrow kit has everything you need to keep your brows looking on point. The kit includes 4 universally flattering shades for all brow tones a slanted eyebrow brush an eyebrow comb and 3 different stencils to help you get the perfect shape for your face. Now you can fill define and shape your brows like never before!', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw2636bb00/ProductImages/Eyes/Eyebrow_Kit_with_Stencils/800897142957_eyebrowkitstencil_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:32:56.029Z', '2017-12-24T02:32:56.324Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/eyebrow-kit-with-stencil/NYX_033.html?cgid=brows'),
(987, 'Eyebrow Marker', 'nyx', '9.75', 0, 'eyebrow', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#4D2712\",\"colour_name\":\"Deep\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#8B6534\",\"colour_name\":\"Medium\"}]', 'Sculpt fill in and enhance your natural eyebrows with our felt-tip Eyebrow Marker. The color resists smearing and smudging and wears all day long.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwe10bfffa/ProductImages/Eyes/Eyebrow_Marker/eyebrowmarker_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:32:56.532Z', '2017-12-24T02:32:56.924Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/eyebrow-marker/NYX_034.html?cgid=brows'),
(988, 'Super Luscious Mascara', 'nyx', '7.0', 0, 'mascara', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#101010\",\"colour_name\":\"More To Love\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#373737\",\"colour_name\":\"Full Figured\"},{\"hex_value\":\"gray7\",\"colour_name\":\"Voluptuous\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#191919\",\"colour_name\":\"Curvaceous\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#0E0E0E\",\"colour_name\":\"Badunkadunk\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#252525\",\"colour_name\":\"XXL\"}]', 'Everyone will notice your gorgeous lashes with our Super Luscious Mascara Collection. Featuring seven different brushes, each fragrance-free mascara has something unique to offer. (Plus, they’re formulated with keratins, vitamins and naturally-derived waxes to nourish lashes!) There’s a Super Luscious Mascara for your essential lash looks.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw97d7c9f2/ProductImages/Eyes/Super_Luscious_Mascara/superlusciousmascara_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:32:57.547Z', '2017-12-24T02:32:57.912Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/super-luscious-mascara/NYX_122.html?cgid=mascara'),
(989, 'Color Mascara', 'nyx', '7.0', 0, 'mascara', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#F5F3F4\",\"colour_name\":\"Pink Petals\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#F7F5F8\",\"colour_name\":\"Forget Me Not\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#F4FAF6\",\"colour_name\":\"Mint Julep\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#FBFAF6\",\"colour_name\":\"Coral Reef\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#FEFBF6\",\"colour_name\":\"Perfect Pear\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#FFF9F3\",\"colour_name\":\"Brown\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#FBFCFF\",\"colour_name\":\"Blue\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#FFFAFF\",\"colour_name\":\"Purple\"}]', 'Think beyond the ordinary with these fun and vibrant new mascara options from NYX Professional Makeup. Packed full of pigments and delivering on the promise of intense color payoff, everyone will notice your fabulous eye lash color. Go for it - we dare you to try all eight shades!', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw8044f7e7/ProductImages/Eyes/Color_Mascara/colormascara_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:32:59.193Z', '2017-12-24T02:32:59.610Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/color-mascara/NYX_124.html?cgid=mascara'),
(990, 'Boudoir Mascara Collection', 'nyx', '6.0', 0, 'mascara', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#121212\",\"colour_name\":\"Za Za Zu\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#2B2B2B\",\"colour_name\":\"La Amoureux\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#151515\",\"colour_name\":\"Le Chick Flick\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#141414\",\"colour_name\":\"Faux Lashes\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#0D0D0D\",\"colour_name\":\"Provocateur\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#232323\",\"colour_name\":\"Pin-Up Tease\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#131315\",\"colour_name\":\"Le Frou Frou\"}]', 'Every powder room should have our luxurious Boudoir Mascara Collection available in 7 elite formulas. Whether you want to darken, amp up the volume, or lengthen your lashes - we have a mascara that meets all your needs.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwda9f6cec/ProductImages/Eyes/Boudoir_Mascara_Collection/boudoirmascaracollection_main.jpg.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:33:00.623Z', '2017-12-24T02:33:01.097Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/boudoir-mascara-collection/NYX_060.html?cgid=mascara'),
(991, 'Worth the Hype Volumizing & Lengthening Mascara', 'nyx', '8.0', 0, 'mascara', '[]', 'Take our word for it: if you want your lashes to look darker, fuller and lethally gorgeous all day long, then our new Worth the Hype Volumizing & Lengthening Mascara is your jam. A breeze to apply and comfortable to wear, this buildable formula actually does what it promises, making it “worth the hype” in every which way. It also features a brush that tapers at the tip, so you can brush, build, and lengthen even the littlest baby lashes at the inner corners of your eyes.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwb654afff/ProductImages/2018/Eyes/Worth_The_Hype_Volumizing_Mascara/800897140250_worththehypevolumizingmascara_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:33:02.251Z', '2017-12-24T02:33:02.648Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/worth-the-hype-volumizing-lengthening-mascara/NYX_590.html?cgid=mascara'),
(992, 'The Skinny Mascara', 'nyx', '7.0', 0, 'mascara', '[]', 'Our ultra-skinny mascara brush is perfect for coating hard to reach lashes from root to tipâ€”even along the bottom lash line! Finally the smallest, thinnest lashes can get extra special attention too. The water resistant formula and micro brush work together to create the appearance of long beautifully defined lashes.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dwcb91e11f/ProductImages/Eyes/The_Skinny_Mascara/theskinnymascara_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:33:02.793Z', '2017-12-24T02:33:04.446Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/the-skinny-mascara/NYX_183.html?cgid=mascara'),
(993, 'Doll Eye Mascara', 'nyx', '9.5', 0, 'mascara', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#141414\",\"colour_name\":\"Waterproof - Black\"}]', 'Hello, dollface! For irresistibly fluttery eyelashes, try this mascara on for size. Doll Eye Mascara uses a unique blend of natural oil and nylon fibers to extend lashes to almost faux proportions. Choose from our Doll Eye Mascara in Long Lash, Volume or Waterproof.', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/dw/image/v2/AANG_PRD/on/demandware.static/-/Sites-cpd-nyxusa-master-catalog/default/dw2e036256/ProductImages/Eyes/Doll_Eye_Mascara/800897123543_dolleyemascara_longlash_black_main.jpg?sw=390&sh=390&sm=fit', '2017-12-24T02:33:04.665Z', '2017-12-24T02:33:05.096Z', 'https://www.nyxcosmetics.com/doll-eye-mascara/NYX_017.html?cgid=mascara'),
