(1021, 'Gel Liner', 'marienatie', '0.0', 0, 'eyeliner', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#000000\",\"colour_name\":\"Black\"}]', 'This smooth and creamy formula from MarieNatie will provide a silky soft and non-oily finish. It glides on evenly to deliver immediate results.', 'https://www.purpicks.com/wp-content/uploads/csm/Photo10_12001.jpg', '2018-06-30T19:19:30.898Z', '2018-09-02T22:52:06.494Z', 'https://www.purpicks.com/product/marie-natie-gel-liner/'),
(1022, 'Lip Gloss', 'marienatie', '0.0', 0, 'lipstick', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#CA5774\",\"colour_name\":\"Wild\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D37B92\",\"colour_name\":\"Babe\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#F1B8BE\",\"colour_name\":\"Pure\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#99696C\",\"colour_name\":\"Lush\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#8B5B5F\",\"colour_name\":\"Envy\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E89EA2\",\"colour_name\":\"Tickled\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D5A3A1\",\"colour_name\":\"Flair\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D5A291\",\"colour_name\":\"Posh\"}]', 'MarieNatie offers a gluten free and vegan lip gloss providing rich colours and shine without the stickiness. The natural oils will offer moisturizing properties and lasting hydration for your lips. Contains grape seed oil to reduce aging and wrinkles and sunflower oil has the ability to heal skin. Vitamin E is a great antioxidant that will protect and repair skin.', 'https://www.purpicks.com/wp-content/uploads/csm/Envy1.jpg', '2018-06-30T19:19:30.964Z', '2018-09-02T22:52:06.502Z', 'https://www.purpicks.com/product/lip-gloss/'),
(1023, 'Lipstick', 'marienatie', '0.0', 0, 'lipstick', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#B4556E\",\"colour_name\":\"Ava\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#9A1C24\",\"colour_name\":\"Giselle\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#B03B3E\",\"colour_name\":\"Rosie\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#9D5E4F\",\"colour_name\":\"Evelyn\"}]', 'A pure and creamy lipstick by MarieNatie formulated with organic jojoba, avocado, and coconut oil which are rich in anti-oxidants and have moisturizing benefits. Enriched with naturally derived organic mango and cocoa butters that will soothe, hydrate and regenerate dry lips.', 'https://www.purpicks.com/wp-content/uploads/csm/Evelyn_Pic1.jpg', '2018-06-30T19:19:31.034Z', '2018-09-02T22:52:06.510Z', 'https://www.purpicks.com/product/marie-natie-lipstick/'),
(1024, 'Loose Mineral Eyeshadow', 'marienatie', '0.0', 0, 'eyeshadow', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#47404A\",\"colour_name\":\"Noir\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#8B5966\",\"colour_name\":\"Mauve\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#B0A9AC\",\"colour_name\":\"Argent\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#F8DDAE\",\"colour_name\":\"Oro\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#808193\",\"colour_name\":\"Aubergine\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#AB9A9E\",\"colour_name\":\"Riz Violet\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#8D6255\",\"colour_name\":\"Chocolate\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#C57F70\",\"colour_name\":\"Oam\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#92A281\",\"colour_name\":\"Emerald\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#9F9686\",\"colour_name\":\"K aki\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#CBD0D0\",\"colour_name\":\"Jade\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E4C2C4\",\"colour_name\":\"Rose\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D1A390\",\"colour_name\":\"Bisque\"}]', 'Long-lasting eye colours delivering an instant glam and shimmer.  Silky and soft texture of MarieNatie glides on easily when applied wet or dry.  Magnesium stearate repels water and will help keep your eye shadow on all day and absorb any extra oil.  Kaolin clay will help to purify, soothe different skin types.', 'https://www.purpicks.com/wp-content/uploads/csm/Loose_MineralEyeshadow_1024x1024_a958d62b-c518-4548-a2cd-9c8981f5edee1.jpg', '2018-06-30T19:19:31.101Z', '2018-09-02T22:52:06.518Z', 'https://www.purpicks.com/product/marie-natie-loose-mineral-eyeshadow/'),
(1025, 'Perfect Lash Mascara', 'marienatie', '0.0', 0, 'mascara', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#000000\",\"colour_name\":\"Black\"}]', 'Marie Natie Perfect Lash Mascara is made with all natural ingredients that will not only condition your lashes but lengthen and thicken your every lash with every stroke.  Oregano, rosemary and thyme extract are great antioxidants and helps to maintain skin health.  Cinnamon bark extracts helps to fight infection.  Lemon peel extract contains natural healing and soothing properties.', 'https://www.purpicks.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/marie-natie-perfect-lash-mascara.png', '2018-06-30T19:19:31.192Z', '2018-09-02T22:52:06.828Z', 'https://www.purpicks.com/product/marie-natie-perfect-lash-mascara/');
