(1026, 'Mineral Blush', 'marienatie', '0.0', 0, 'blush', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#DF9A84\",\"colour_name\":\"Desert Rose\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#C97D66\",\"colour_name\":\"Blushing Apple\"}]', 'Formulated to reduce the appearance of pores while creating a long-lasting natural finish.  This MarieNatie brush protects skin with SPF15.  Sericite mica is great for absorbing oil and won’t clog up pores.  Mica is a natural mineral that helps to enhance the skin tone.', 'https://www.purpicks.com/wp-content/uploads/csm/Blush_copy_1024x1024_edd99d6d-301e-4ba1-aa74-a33d21147b7c1.jpg', '2018-06-30T19:19:31.234Z', '2018-09-02T22:52:06.590Z', 'https://www.purpicks.com/product/marie-natie-mineral-blush/'),
(1028, 'Pressed Foundation', 'marienatie', '0.0', 0, 'foundation', '[{\"hex_value\":\"#C29F90\",\"colour_name\":\"Deep Golden\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D8AD91\",\"colour_name\":\"Chocolate\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#D4AD8C\",\"colour_name\":\"Caramel\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#F4D3B8\",\"colour_name\":\"Honey\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#E7C09D\",\"colour_name\":\"Tan\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#F3D2B7\",\"colour_name\":\"Warm Tan\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#FAE3C9\",\"colour_name\":\"Sunny Beige\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#ECBFA3\",\"colour_name\":\"Natural Beige\"},{\"hex_value\":\"#F8DBC3\",\"colour_name\":\"Ivory\"}]', 'A pressed foundation by MarieNatie providing a silky and flawless finish – it provides great coverage and protects skin with SPF 10.  Titanium dioxide acts as an absorbent of oil and jojoba oil helps to cleanse and moisturize the skin.', 'https://www.purpicks.com/wp-content/uploads/csm/caramel_1024x1024_e5fbf151-0cfd-42c9-a5ec-f49d6104bcbc1.jpg', '2018-06-30T19:19:31.368Z', '2018-09-02T22:52:06.609Z', 'https://www.purpicks.com/product/marie-natie-pressed-foundation/'),
